{"reponsecode":0,"reponsemessage":"","data":{"ispaid":1,"exhibit_id":"XMT_hytssnt","exhibition_name":"展览二区","location":"509,674","name":"红叶题诗仕女图","size":"明 纵104cm，横47cm","like":2,"share_url":"mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=87","share_url2":"https://share.morview.com/#/share?id=XMT_hytssnt","is_favorited":0,"_3d_url":"","description":"唐寅，1470年至1523年，字伯虎，又字子畏，以字行，号六如居士、桃花庵主、鲁国唐生、逃禅仙吏等，吴县吴趋里人。众多字号中以“伯虎”为大众所熟知。作为明朝著名的画家、诗人，唐寅为后世留下了众多优秀的作品。这幅《红叶题诗仕女图》以传统的工笔重彩的手法，以“三白法”染仕女的面部，突出了宫女的浓妆艳抹。衣纹用流畅的铁线描，服饰施以浓艳的色彩，显得绮罗绚烂。把宫妓们竞相装扮，斗绿争绯的情态刻画得生动入微，不愧为唐寅仕女画的优秀之作。","images":["content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/KosFpxiLR_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/KosFpxiLR1_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/KosFpxiLR2_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/KosFpxiLR3_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/KosFpxiLR4_s.webp"],"audio":[{"audiotype":"mandarin","filename":"content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/audio/3BP11b5Em8.mp3"}],"video":{"videourl":"","img":""}}}